SABELO NSELE AKANALO itwetwe ngemiphumela ka-matric uNgqongqoshe wezeMfundo KwaZulu-Natal, uKwazi Mshengu, yize ukufunda kuphazamiseke ngezinyanga ezintathu ngenxa yeCorona. ukufund. UBA  ukufunda kuphazamiseke ngezinyanga ezintathu kulo nyaka, uNgqongqoshe wezeMfundo KwaZulu-Natal uMnuz Kwazi Mshengu, akanatwetwe ngemiphumela kamatric. Ngeledlule abafundi baka-matric abangaphezu kwesigidi baqalile ukubhala izivivinyo zokuphela konyaka. UMshengu uvakashele isikole eMgungundlovu, iNyonithwele Secondary, ukuyohlola ukuthi konke kuhamba kahle yini. Bangaphezu kuka-129 000 abafundi kulesi sifundazwe ababhale isiNgisi.eSingisi. Ekhuluma nabezindaba, uMshengu uthe akalindele ukuthi ukuphazamiseka kokufunda okwaba khona ngesikhathi sikathaqa, kube nomthelela ongemuhle endleleni abafundi baKwaZulu-Natal abazokwenza ngayo kulezi zivivinyo. “Sisebenze kanzima ukwenza isiqiniseko sokuthi abafundi bayakwazi ukufunda lokho obekufanele engabe bakufunde ngesikhathi sikathaqa. Siphinde sasebenza kanzima ukusindisa impilo yabo kuleli gciwane. “Asilindele ukuthi kube khona izikole ezingeke zenze kahle. Ngokwethu sifisa engabe sibe nesikhathi esithe xaxa ukuze sicije kahle abafundi bethu. Ngebhadi isikhathi esibe naso yisona esisitholile, sabe sesenza okusemandleni ethu.” Ngonyaka owedlule kulesi sifundazwe izinga lokuphasa ku-matric libe ngaphezu kuka- 81%. UMshengu uthe bekunzima ukulungiselela izivivinyo ngoba iCorona ayikanqotshwa. “Siningi kakhulu isikhathi esilahlekile njengoba ukufunda kwamiswa ngoMashi. Sathi noma sesiqalile ngoJuni, kwaba nobuhixihixi njengoba bekubuye kumiswe ukufunda. Lesi simo esibhekane naso sinzima kakhulu kwezike sabhekana nazo selokhu kwaba unyaka ka-1994. “Siyakubonga ukuzimisela kothisha nabafundi abenze isiqiniseko sokuthi bayeza esikoleni nakuba isimo besinzima. Kuphoqeleke ukuthi bafunde izinsuku eziyisikhombisa ngesonto, kuzanywa ukuhlenga lo nyaka wezemfundo.” UMshengu uthe sebekhiphe umyalelo wokuthi abafundi baka-matric beze esikoleni nangezinsuku abangafundi ngazo ukuze bacijwe ukuthi balungele ukubhala izivivinyo ezilandelayo. 